install_msg:
Thanks for installing. Remember this cog constain hard, sad and dep quotes, Do me a favor and uninstall this directly if you cannot handle sad, dep and hard quotes that can quote alot of yourself.. Do remember you're not alone, no matter what. Sending you a big hug.

You can disable mentions from `[p]qset set`.
